    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly starter? This vehicle is ready for some TLC! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves and restore a car to its former glory. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price and make it your own!",
